      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "FINE VIEW (8) was a last start winner (19.80) at this track who is building a strong winning record. Has never been out of the money in seven starts this course and distance. Unbeaten from this box in two starts. The hardest to beat again. ZING MATILDA (1) had a tricky draw last time and although midfield in fourth wasn't far away finishing 2 lengths from the winner (20.26). Solid record here at the distance winning six races. A forward showing wouldn't surprise. ZIPPING THERON (2) finds it hard to win. Finished third (31.91) at Gawler latest and might be close to finding winning form again. Can measure up. STELLA SWIFT (6) is fresh from a short break and ready to run well.",
